Depends:
 ${misc:Depends}, bash, figlet, lolcat, fastfetch
Description: Linux maintenance and cache cleaning utility
 Ghostwipe automates package updates, cache cleanup,
 temporary file removal, journal maintenance, and
 routine housekeeping tasks for Debian-based systems.
 .
 It provides both standard maintenance operations and
 advanced cleanup options through an interactive
 terminal interface.
